@startuml Artifact Lineage Overview
title Artifact Lineage Overview
!include architecture-theme.puml

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

artifact raw_data_snapshot as "Raw Data Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact interim_dataset_snapshot as "Interim Dataset Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact processed_dataset_snapshot as "Processed Dataset Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact feature_set_snapshot as "Feature Set Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact search_run_snapshot as "Search Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact train_run_snapshot as "Train Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact evaluation_run_snapshot as "Evaluation Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact explainability_run_snapshot as "Explainability Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact promotion_run_snapshot as "Promotion Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact inference_run_snapshot as "Inference Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>
artifact monitoring_run_snapshot as "Monitoring Run Snapshot" <<artifact>>

raw_data_snapshot --> interim_dataset_snapshot
interim_dataset_snapshot --> processed_dataset_snapshot
processed_dataset_snapshot --> feature_set_snapshot
feature_set_snapshot --> search_run_snapshot

search_run_snapshot --> train_run_snapshot
train_run_snapshot --> evaluation_run_snapshot
train_run_snapshot --> explainability_run_snapshot
evaluation_run_snapshot --> promotion_run_snapshot
explainability_run_snapshot --> promotion_run_snapshot
promotion_run_snapshot --> inference_run_snapshot
inference_run_snapshot --> monitoring_run_snapshot

note right of feature_set_snapshot
Input and derived schemas are stored at
the version level (same across all snapshots)
end note

note right of search_run_snapshot
Creates a new experiment
end note

legend right
-->   Artifact lineage / flow
endlegend

@enduml